# miniClaude — auth priority (auto-detected at startup):
#
# 1. Claude Code subscription (FREE if you have a Pro/Max plan)
#    Just be logged into Claude Code on this machine. miniClaude pulls
#    the OAuth token out of macOS Keychain or ~/.claude/.credentials.json.
#    No env vars needed.
#
# 2. ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN — any OAuth Bearer token (paste manually)
#
# 3. ANTHROPIC_API_KEY    — direct Anthropic API billing (sk-ant-...)
#
# 4. OPENROUTER_API_KEY   — OpenRouter route (cheap / free model fallback)
#
# Set whichever you have; the first one found wins.

# --- Claude Code OAuth route (manual paste; route 1 is auto) ---
# ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN=
# ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=https://api.anthropic.com
# ANTHROPIC_MODEL=claude-sonnet-4-5

# --- Direct Anthropic API ---
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
# ANTHROPIC_MODEL=claude-sonnet-4-5

# --- OpenRouter fallback ---
OPENROUTER_API_KEY=
OPENROUTER_MODEL=anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5
